{"type":"message","id":"150df1f2","parentId":"014a5e6c","timestamp":"2026-06-03T00:27:55.794Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The config looks fine. Let me just update the timeout on the Son cron job to 600s as a first step. The user said \"不是都修改成300了吗\" - so they set it to 300 already. Let me bump it to 600.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"先给你改到 600s 试试，要是还超就真要精简内容了。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_w17kyaXOtA3RIIPypAJN4246","name":"cron","arguments":{"action":"update","jobId":"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678","patch":{"payload":{"kind":"agentTurn","message":"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation","timeoutSeconds":600}}},"partialArgs":"{\"action\": \"update\", \"jobId\": \"557cdce4-3315-41d0-a7c9-37f069050678\", \"patch\": {\"payload\": {\"kind\": \"agentTurn\", \"message\": \"[morningcourt] sender_id=6687D4D2D1F8EDA5231C6809B1A26204, trigger briefing generation\", \"timeoutSeconds\": 600}}}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":147,"output":222,"cacheRead":29696,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":54,"totalTokens":30065,"cost":{"input":0.000020580000000000003,"output":0.00006216,"cacheRead":0.000831488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.000914228}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780446473873,"responseId":"e28155c2-617e-47fd-bcba-6b6475bb6610"}}
