{"type":"message","id":"40c598c7","parentId":"dd83ff66","timestamp":"2026-06-03T02:58:25.467Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking whether the dreaming run will snowball (get progressively slower over time) — since it processes all users every day and might accumulate more and more data. Let me think about this.\n\nThe dreaming process:\n1. Reads heart/background.md, identity.md, state.md, dreams.md — these are fixed-size files\n2. Iterates over each user directory\n3. For each user: reads encountings.md and impressions.md, then reads the latest session history (.jsonl files)\n4. Updates encountings.md (appends), possibly compresses if > 20 entries\n5. Updates state.md (fixed size)\n\nThe main concern would be:\n1. **Number of users growing** — more users = more iterations\n2. **Session history growing** — .jsonl files getting bigger over time\n3. **encountings.md growing** — but there's a compression rule (>20 entries → compress to impressions.md, keep last 5)\n\nLet me check how many users there are currently and how big the session files are.\n\nThe dreaming has a compression mechanism for encountings.md (>20 → compress, keep 5). So that won't grow unbounded.\n\nThe session .jsonl files — these are the actual conversation transcripts. They do grow over time. But Son's morningcourt reads session history too.\n\nLet me check what the current state is.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"应该不会。来看看实际数据量："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CwwvnqJpaukHOLcJpPww0798","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo \"=== 用户数量 ===\" && ls -d ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l && echo \"=== 各用户 session 文件大小 ===\" && find ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/ -name \"*.jsonl\" -exec ls -lh {} \\; 2>/dev/null | awk '{print $5, $NF}' && echo \"=== encountings.md 行数 ===\" && for f in ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/encountings.md; do echo \"$(wc -l < \"$f\")行 $(dirname \"$f\" | xargs basename)\"; done 2>/dev/null"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"echo \\\"=== 用户数量 ===\\\" && ls -d ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/ 2>/dev/null | wc -l && echo \\\"=== 各用户 session 文件大小 ===\\\" && find ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/ -name \\\"*.jsonl\\\" -exec ls -lh {} \\\\; 2>/dev/null | awk '{print $5, $NF}' && echo \\\"=== encountings.md 行数 ===\\\" && for f in ~/.openclaw/workspace-father/users/*/encountings.md; do echo \\\"$(wc -l < \\\"$f\\\")行 $(dirname \\\"$f\\\" | xargs basename)\\\"; done 2>/dev/null\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2754,"output":488,"cacheRead":30336,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":283,"totalTokens":33578,"cost":{"input":0.00038556,"output":0.00013664000000000002,"cacheRead":0.000849408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0013716079999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780455500288,"responseId":"e24689c1-f5ce-4c9a-b59e-5b172e257c53"}}
