{"type":"message","id":"8b851a77","parentId":"6e66e0be","timestamp":"2026-06-03T04:23:46.580Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑发给了一张截图，内容是微博/X上一条\"串文\"（搞笑段子）：一个人跟女同学散步，看到两条狗在交配，女同学尴尬地问\"你有没有类似的想法\"，他赶紧说\"我对母狗没兴趣\"。\n\n这是一条搞笑段子的截图，汀桑就是分享给我看的，没有什么功能触发。我随便回复一下就好。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"又拿这种段子来荼毒我眼睛😓\n\n这哥们反应够快的，「我对母狗没兴趣」——一秒把自己摘干净了🍧"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1927,"output":111,"cacheRead":32768,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":77,"totalTokens":34806,"cost":{"input":0.00026978,"output":0.00003108,"cacheRead":0.000917504,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001218364}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780460624444,"responseId":"6d60bf30-fd5e-4f40-a71e-b0df08b0e4bc"}}
