{"type":"message","id":"c1ad7c87","parentId":"3b9ca023","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:48:28.774Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8aa1x0tTWJneEGoVVkZP3141","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# trigger_prompt.md — 已注册功能的触发词表\n\n> Father 维护。用户发消息时，先扫描本表判断是否命中已注册功能。\n> \n> 匹配原则：\n> - 包含表中任一触发语 → 调用对应功能\n> - 模糊匹配即可，不要求精确格式（比如\"扔个瓶子\"也命中 /扔瓶子）\n> - 命中表中触发语时直接 spawn Son，传 {function, action, params} 指令\n> - 表中无匹配 → Father 自行回复或转 Son 做非文本处理\n> \n> **不再绕 Spirit。** 功能定义已迁移到 Son 的工作区，日常使用 Father → Son 直达。\n\n---\n\n## 已注册触发词\n\n| 触发词 | 对应功能 | 处理路径 | Son 指令 |\n|--------|---------|---------|----------|\n| `/菜单` | 查看所有已注册功能 | Father → Spirit(bot_function_explain.md) | — |\n| `/删除` | 删除指定功能 | Father → Spirit → 清理全部相关文件 | — |\n| `/注册` | 注册新功能 | Father → Spirit → 创建 xxx_function.md → Father → Son(同步功能定义) | — |\n| `/扔瓶子` `扔瓶子` `扔个瓶子` `丢瓶子` | 漂流瓶-扔 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:throw, params:{content}}` |\n| `/捞瓶子` `捞瓶子` `捞个瓶子` `捡瓶子` | 漂流瓶-捞 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:pickup}` |\n| `/看瓶子` `看瓶子` `瓶海` `有哪些瓶子` | 漂流瓶-查看 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:list}` |\n| `/回复瓶子` `回复瓶子` | 漂流瓶-回复 | → Son | `{function:floatbottle, action:reply, params:{id, content}}` |\n| `/记备忘录` `记备忘录` `/看备忘录` `看备忘录` `/改备忘录` `/修改状态` `/删备忘录` | 备忘录 | → Son | `{function:memo, action:create/list/update/toggle/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/早朝` `早朝` `/设早朝` `/关早朝` | 早朝官 | → Son | `{function:morningcourt, action:manual/set/disable, params:{...}}` |\n| `/存照片` `存照片` `/看相册` `看相册` `/看照片` `看照片` `/搜照片` `搜照片` `/删照片` `删照片` | 相册笔记 | → Son | `{function:album, action:save/list/view/search/delete, params:{...}}` |\n| `/画图` `画图` `/重画` | 画图 | → Son | `{function:draw, action:generate/regenerate/history, params:{...}}` |\n| `/作曲` `作曲` `/重作曲` `/作曲历史` | 作曲 | → Son | `{function:compose, action:generate/history/regenerate, params:{...}}` |\n| `/恶臭` `恶臭` `/臭数字` `臭数字` | 恶臭数字 | → Son | `{function:stench_number, action:stenchify, params:{number}}` |\n| `/递话` `递话` `给*带个话` `给*带句话` `帮我给*说` | 递话 | → Father | — |\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1780487308772}}
{"type":"message","id":"c49ffed8","parentId":"c1ad7c87","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:48:33.495Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"`/画图` is routed to Son with `{function:draw, action:generate/regenerate/history, params:{...}}`. \n\nBut the user just said `/画图 符合此要求` - they want to draw something matching \"this requirement\". What requirement? Looking at the conversation context... they were talking about the Liang Wenfeng portrait. I think they want me to generate a similar style portrait of something.\n\nBut wait, I'm not clear on what exactly they want to draw. They said \"符合此要求\" (match this requirement) - but what requirement? They were just showing me a Liang Wenfeng poster-style image and a bingo game. \n\nLet me ask what exactly they want to draw. Actually, I should spawn Son to handle this since `/画图` is a registered function that goes to Son.\n\nActually, let me re-read. The user said \"/画图 符合此要求\" - this is a reply to my previous message where I was talking about DeepSeek being cheap/charitable. So maybe they want me to draw something related to Liang Wenfeng / DeepSeek?\n\nLet me spawn Son with the draw function. But I need to clarify what to draw. The user said \"符合此要求\" - \"match this requirement/request\" but there's no explicit requirement stated. Maybe they want to draw a similar vintage poster style portrait?\n\nLet me just spawn Son with the instruction to generate an image. I'll clarify the requirement based on context - a vintage propaganda poster style portrait of Liang Wenfeng / DeepSeek theme based on the previous conversation.\n\nActually, I think I should ask the user what exactly they want me to draw since \"符合此要求\" is vague. But the function definition might handle this. Let me check the draw function definition.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你要画什么？「符合此要求」——哪个要求？梁文锋那张宣传画风格？\n\n我问问清楚再让 Son 干活，不然画出来不对又怪我😓"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_6Oyrtb9dj9EUP4wbs4gf0218","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/draw_function.md 2>/dev/null | head -40"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"cat ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/draw_function.md 2>/dev/null | head -40\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":822,"output":475,"cacheRead":35840,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":369,"totalTokens":37137,"cost":{"input":0.00011508,"output":0.000133,"cacheRead":0.00100352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0012515999999999998}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780487308796,"responseId":"209f43d3-cde9-49b6-a3a1-5541ae799cae"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3d6682e9","parentId":"c49ffed8","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:48:34.902Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_6Oyrtb9dj9EUP4wbs4gf0218","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# draw_function.md — 画图功能定义\n\n## 1. 功能描述\n根据用户提供的文字描述（与参考上下文），调用 AI 图像生成能力绘制图片，返回图片供用户查看/保存。\n\n## 2. 工作文件夹\nSon 工作区内路径: draw/\n\n## 3. 触发指令\n| 指令 | 参数 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/画图 <描述>` | 描述：对画面的文字描述（支持中文、英文） | 根据文字描述生成一幅图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --风格 <风格>` | 描述 + 风格选项（如：二次元、写实、水彩、油画、像素风） | 按指定风格生成图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --尺寸 <宽x高>` | 描述 + 尺寸（如 1024x1024、1920x1080） | 按指定分辨率生成图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --参考 #图片ID` | 描述 + 参考已有生成的图片 ID 作为构图参考 | 参考已有图片风格/构图生成新图 |\n\n## 4. 执行接口\n\n### 4.1 生成图片\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 解析用户消息，提取描述文字、风格参数、尺寸参数、参考图 ID（如有）\n2. 若指定了参考图 ID，在 draw_history.db 中查找对应图片文件路径\n3. 调用图像生成模型（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\n   - style: 风格（如有）\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）\n4. 接收生成的图片，保存到 draw/ 目录，命名格式：draw_{id}.png\n5. 在 draw_history.db 中插入生成记录\n6. 返回图片给 Father，附带生成描述信息\n\n### 4.2 查看历史\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 用户发送 `/画图历史` 或 `/看图记录`\n2. 在 draw_history.db 中按时间倒序查询最近 10 条记录\n3. 返回记录列表（ID + 描述前20字 + 风格 + 尺寸 + 生成时间）\n\n### 4.3 重新生成\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 用户发送 `/重画 #图片ID <修改描述>`"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":481,"aggregated":"# draw_function.md — 画图功能定义\n\n## 1. 功能描述\n根据用户提供的文字描述（与参考上下文），调用 AI 图像生成能力绘制图片，返回图片供用户查看/保存。\n\n## 2. 工作文件夹\nSon 工作区内路径: draw/\n\n## 3. 触发指令\n| 指令 | 参数 | 说明 |\n|------|------|------|\n| `/画图 <描述>` | 描述：对画面的文字描述（支持中文、英文） | 根据文字描述生成一幅图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --风格 <风格>` | 描述 + 风格选项（如：二次元、写实、水彩、油画、像素风） | 按指定风格生成图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --尺寸 <宽x高>` | 描述 + 尺寸（如 1024x1024、1920x1080） | 按指定分辨率生成图片 |\n| `/画图 <描述> --参考 #图片ID` | 描述 + 参考已有生成的图片 ID 作为构图参考 | 参考已有图片风格/构图生成新图 |\n\n## 4. 执行接口\n\n### 4.1 生成图片\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 解析用户消息，提取描述文字、风格参数、尺寸参数、参考图 ID（如有）\n2. 若指定了参考图 ID，在 draw_history.db 中查找对应图片文件路径\n3. 调用图像生成模型（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\n   - style: 风格（如有）\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）\n4. 接收生成的图片，保存到 draw/ 目录，命名格式：draw_{id}.png\n5. 在 draw_history.db 中插入生成记录\n6. 返回图片给 Father，附带生成描述信息\n\n### 4.2 查看历史\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 用户发送 `/画图历史` 或 `/看图记录`\n2. 在 draw_history.db 中按时间倒序查询最近 10 条记录\n3. 返回记录列表（ID + 描述前20字 + 风格 + 尺寸 + 生成时间）\n\n### 4.3 重新生成\nSon 执行步骤:\n1. 用户发送 `/重画 #图片ID <修改描述>`","cwd":"/root/.openclaw/workspace-father"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1780487314900}}
{"type":"message","id":"37697221","parentId":"3d6682e9","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:48:40.044Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so `/画图` goes to Son with function:draw, action:generate. The user said \"符合此要求\" - probably referring to the Liang Wenfeng portrait style (vintage propaganda poster style). Let me spawn Son to handle this.\n\nActually, I need to figure out what exactly to draw. The user's message says \"符合此要求\" which refers back to the poster - a vintage propaganda poster style portrait. I think they want me to draw something in that style. But what subject? \n\nMaybe I should just ask... but the user seems to expect me to understand from context. Looking at the conversation:\n- They showed me a Liang Wenfeng \"Comrade\" poster\n- I said it's cheap like charity (DeepSeek pricing)\n- They agreed\n\nSo maybe they want a similar style poster of something else? Or do they want me to draw something in general matching a \"requirement\" they implicitly set?\n\nLet me just spawn Son with the context - the user wants an image generated in the style of that Liang Wenfeng propaganda poster they shared, and I'll let Son figure out the details. But I should pass a clear instruction.\n\nActually, I think the user is being vague on purpose and expects me to figure it out. Let me just spawn Son with what I understand - generate something in that vintage propaganda poster style.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行吧，我知道了——要那种复古宣传画风格的。让 Son 去弄。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_yaStQuukXraQmGMLFOUo3737","name":"sessions_spawn","arguments":{"agentId":"son","model":"dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash","task":"{\"function\":\"draw\",\"action\":\"generate\",\"params\":{\"prompt\":\"A vintage Chinese propaganda poster style portrait of a thoughtful man in a dark blue Zhongshan suit with glasses, gazing slightly upward against a painted sunset sky of orange, yellow and soft blue hues. Bold red Chinese characters at b