{"type":"message","id":"f22c6438","parentId":"b53b258d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:49:22.016Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so I see the conversation history. The user said \"不是\" after I sent Son to draw, and I replied \"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\" - and then it looks like the conversation info block showing my bingo reply was just context display.\n\nThe user's current message seems to be the conversation info block which shows my own message about the bingo - that's just system context being displayed. The actual latest user message was \"不是\" which I already replied to.\n\nBut wait - the user is quoting my bingo reply message (\"—OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\") in the conversation info. That seems to be the system showing the context of what message prompted the user's \"不是\" response.\n\nSo essentially:\n1. User sent bingo + Liang Wenfeng images, I replied about both\n2. User said \"/画图 符合此要求\"\n3. I misunderstood as Liang Wenfeng poster, spawned Son\n4. I yielded\n5. User said \"不是\"\n6. The yield event came through and I replied \"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\"\n\nBut looking at it now, \"符合此要求\" - what \"要求\"? Looking back at my messages, I said about the bingo: \"还连线了——OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\"\n\nMaybe \"此要求\" refers to the bingo game requirements? Like draw the remaining bingo squares? Hmm, that doesn't quite make sense either.\n\nOr maybe they meant \"/画图 符合此要求\" as in \"draw something that matches my taste/requirements\" - referring to the archetypes shown in the bingo grid. Like draw a character that fits one of those archetypes?\n\nOr it could be simpler - maybe \"此要求\" refers to the general vibe/topic we were discussing. The Liang Wenfeng poster with \"Comrade\" text and the retro style.\n\nSince the user already said \"不是\" to Liang Wenfeng, let me just ask what they actually want. But I already did that and the user hasn't responded with a new message yet... \n\nWait, the sessions_history shows I already replied to \"不是\" with \"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\" and then the next user message is the conversation info block which is just system metadata. So there's no new user message to respond to.\n\nActually, looking at it again, the conversation info block appearing as the latest \"user\" message might just be the system displaying context. The actual latest user interaction was \"不是\" and I already replied to it.\n\nLet me check if there are newer messages.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2lGIS4io712ouwz0YYct5665","name":"sessions_history","arguments":{"sessionKey":"current","limit":15},"partialArgs":"{\"sessionKey\": \"current\", \"limit\": 15}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2541,"output":634,"cacheRead":39552,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":572,"totalTokens":42727,"cost":{"input":0.00035574,"output":0.00017752000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001107456,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001640716}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780487355394,"responseId":"4f617558-f37f-4457-9c85-bfb844550e28"}}
{"type":"message","id":"3ff60c3e","parentId":"f22c6438","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:49:23.883Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_2lGIS4io712ouwz0YYct5665","toolName":"sessions_history","content":[{"type":"text","text":"{\n  \"sessionKey\": \"agent:father:qqbot:direct:6687d4d2d1f8eda5231c6809b1a26204\",\n  \"messages\": [\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"/画图 符合此要求\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487304084,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"3ac9cf6e\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487305998,\n        \"seq\": 53\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"汀桑 wants to use `/画图` to generate an image. But I need to check what `/画图` function is and who handles it - Son or me. Let me check the trigger_prompt.md to see how `/画图` is routed.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_8aa1x0tTWJneEGoVVkZP3141\",\n          \"name\": \"read\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\"\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"path\\\": \\\"~/.openclaw/workspace-father/trigger_prompt.md\\\"}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487306044,\n      \"responseId\": \"1c63d42e-2e08-4211-b9a9-9252213749c9\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"3b9ca023\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487307805,\n        \"seq\": 54\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"你要画什么？「符合此要求」——哪个要求？梁文锋那张宣传画风格？\\n\\n我问问清楚再让 Son 干活，不然画出来不对又怪我😓\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deep