 at the conversation flow:\\n1. I said DeepSeek is cheap like charity\\n2. They agreed\\n3. They said \\\"/画图 符合此要求\\\"\\n\\nSo maybe \\\"此要求\\\" refers to something else in the conversation. Let me think about what \\\"要求\\\" (requirement/demand) means here...\\n\\nWait - the last thing I said before they sent /画图 was about DeepSeek being cheap. And before that they showed me the Liang Wenfeng poster and the bingo game.\\n\\nActually, maybe \\\"此要求\\\" refers to... nothing in particular. They might just be saying \\\"draw something that meets this requirement\\\" where the requirement is implicit in the bingo image? Like they want me to draw one of the archetypes from the bingo grid?\\n\\nOr maybe they just meant \\\"/画图\\\" as \\\"let's draw\\\" and \\\"符合此要求\\\" as \\\"meet this standard\\\" - meaning they want a good quality image, not necessarily anything specific?\\n\\nLet me just ask what they want drawn.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"text\",\n          \"text\": \"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\n\\n「符合此要求」——什么要求？你指哪个？\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"stop\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487335201,\n      \"responseId\": \"5f40e90b-a447-4344-95b8-9d079a12e0b5\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"7dd2b692\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487339852,\n        \"seq\": 63\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"user\",\n      \"content\": \"—OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487341521,\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"0f428718\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487343551,\n        \"seq\": 64\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"The user is saying \\\"不是\\\" - not correct. I already responded with \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\" which was the reply to their \\\"不是\\\" message. But looking at the conversation flow, it seems like the system is now showing me the message I already sent as a conversation info block. Actually, this is just the context from the conversation - my previous reply to 汀桑 about the bingo.\\n\\nLet me look at this more carefully. The user said \\\"不是\\\" earlier, and I already replied to that. Now the system is showing me the conversation info which includes my reply. This seems like the conversation continuing after my yield was interrupted by the user's \\\"不是\\\" message.\\n\\nWait, actually the flow is:\\n1. I spawned Son to draw a Liang Wenfeng poster\\n2. I yielded waiting for completion\\n3. User said \\\"不是\\\" (while I was yielded)\\n4. The yield unblocked and sent my reply \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\"\\n5. Now user is replying to that\\n\\nBut the conversation info shows my bingo game reply was the last message? That doesn't make sense. Let me look at what happened.\\n\\nActually I think what happened is:\\n1. I received the second bingo image and the Liang Wenfeng image\\n2. I replied about the bingo and Liang Wenfeng\\n3. User said \\\"/画图 符合此要求\\\"\\n4. I asked what requirement\\n5. I spawned Son with Liang Wenfeng poster style\\n6. I yielded\\n7. The yield completed but the system is now showing me the conversation state with my last reply being the bingo comment\\n\\nHmm, actually looking at the conversation info block, it's showing \\\"Sender (untrusted metadata)\\\" and \\\"Conversation info\\\" - this is just metadata about the current conversation state (the chat context). The user's actual message is \\\"不是\\\" which I need to handle.\\n\\nWait, I already replied to \\\"不是\\\" with \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\". But maybe the user then sent another \\\"不是\\\" or something else?\\n\\nLet me re-read the conversation flow:\\n\\nThe last visible user message is \\\"不是\\\" - which I already replied to. But now there's a new conversation info block showing my bingo reply. So maybe the conversation info is just being shown as context/state of the conversation.\\n\\nActually, looking at this more carefully, I think what happened is:\\n1. The user said \\\"不是\\\" \\n2. I replied \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\"\\n3. Now the user is saying \\\"不是\\\" again? Or this is the same \\\"不是\\\" being shown again?\\n\\nI'm a bit confused about the conversation state. Let me just ask again what they want.\\n\\nActually, looking at the conversation info block, it shows my reply about the bingo - \\\"OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\\\" as the last message in the context. So the user said \\\"不是\\\" after that, and I already replied. But now the conversation continues...\\n\\nWait, I think the issue is that the yield completed and my reply went through, and now the user is continuing the conversation. But I don't see a new user message. Let me check sessions history.\\n\\nActually, the display shows:\\n```\\n[Context: The previous turn ended intentionally via sessions_yield while waiting for a follow-up event.]\\n\\n不是\\n```\\n\\nThen some conversation info blocks showing my bingo reply as context. So the user said \\\"不是\\\" - that's the current message I need to handle. And I already replied... but the conversation info is just showing the context.\\n\\nHmm, I think what's happening is:\\n1. I yielded\\n2. Son's task started but user interrupted with \\\"不是\\\"\\n3. The yield event fired and my reply went through\\n4. Now the user is replying to my \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\"\\n\\nActually no - I think this whole flow might be the conversation replaying. Let me just check what the current user message actually is by looking at sessions history.\\n\\nLet me just ask the user directly what's going on and what they actually want to draw.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_cvNuCZS6BS9fGDsCayo04494\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_history\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"sessionKey\": \"current\",\n            \"limit\": 10\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"current\\\", \\\"limit\\\": 10}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487343616,\n      \"responseId\": \"6f9861b2-1b44-417b-9ac4-72f9245d6fe2\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"be5b3755\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487352781,\n        \"seq\": 65\n      }\n    },\n    {\n      \"role\": \"assistant\",\n      \"content\": [\n        {\n          \"type\": \"thinking\",\n          \"thinking\": \"OK so I see the conversation history. The user said \\\"不是\\\" after I sent Son to draw, and I replied \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\" - and then it looks like the conversation info block showing my bingo reply was just context display.\\n\\nThe user's current message seems to be the conversation info block which shows my own message about the bingo - that's just system context being displayed. The actual latest user message was \\\"不是\\\" which I already replied to.\\n\\nBut wait - the user is quoting my bingo reply message (\\\"—OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\\\") in the conversation info. That seems to be the system showing the context of what message prompted the user's \\\"不是\\\" response.\\n\\nSo essentially:\\n1. User sent bingo + Liang Wenfeng images, I replied about both\\n2. User said \\\"/画图 符合此要求\\\"\\n3. I misunderstood as Liang Wenfeng poster, spawned Son\\n4. I yielded\\n5. User said \\\"不是\\\"\\n6. The yield event came through and I replied \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\"\\n\\nBut looking at it now, \\\"符合此要求\\\" - what \\\"要求\\\"? Looking back at my messages, I said about the bingo: \\\"还连线了——OL、空姐、文学少女……挺会挑啊你。剩下的格子留着下次再战？\\\"\\n\\nMaybe \\\"此要求\\\" refers to the bingo game requirements? Like draw the remaining bingo squares? Hmm, that doesn't quite make sense either.\\n\\nOr maybe they meant \\\"/画图 符合此要求\\\" as in \\\"draw something that matches my taste/requirements\\\" - referring to the archetypes shown in the bingo grid. Like draw a character that fits one of those archetypes?\\n\\nOr it could be simpler - maybe \\\"此要求\\\" refers to the general vibe/topic we were discussing. The Liang Wenfeng poster with \\\"Comrade\\\" text and the retro style.\\n\\nSince the user already said \\\"不是\\\" to Liang Wenfeng, let me just ask what they actually want. But I already did that and the user hasn't responded with a new message yet... \\n\\nWait, the sessions_history shows I already replied to \\\"不是\\\" with \\\"哈？不是梁文锋？那你说清楚啊😓\\\" and then the next user message is the conversation info block which is just system metadata. So there's no new user message to respond to.\\n\\nActually, looking at it again, the conversation info block appearing as the latest \\\"user\\\" message might just be the system displaying context. The actual latest user interaction was \\\"不是\\\" and I already replied to it.\\n\\nLet me check if there are newer messages.\"\n        },\n        {\n          \"type\": \"toolCall\",\n          \"id\": \"call_00_2lGIS4io712ouwz0YYct5665\",\n          \"name\": \"sessions_history\",\n          \"arguments\": {\n            \"sessionKey\": \"current\",\n            \"limit\": 15\n          },\n          \"partialArgs\": \"{\\\"sessionKey\\\": \\\"current\\\", \\\"limit\\\": 15}\"\n        }\n      ],\n      \"api\": \"openai-completions\",\n      \"provider\": \"deepseek\",\n      \"model\": \"deepseek-v4-flash\",\n      \"stopReason\": \"toolUse\",\n      \"timestamp\": 1780487355394,\n      \"responseId\": \"4f617558-f37f-4457-9c85-bfb844550e28\",\n      \"__openclaw\": {\n        \"id\": \"f22c6438\",\n        \"recordTimestampMs\": 1780487362016,\n        \"seq\": 67\n      }\n    }\n  ],\n  \"truncated\": true,\n  \"droppedMessages\": false,\n  \"contentTruncated\": true,\n  \"contentRedacted\": false,\n  \"bytes\": 11637\n}"}],"details":{"persistedDetailsTruncated":true,"orig