{"type":"message","id":"74d69afc","parentId":"0603ef8d","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:52:11.667Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK so 汀桑 is saying he only wanted ONE picture - the one I originally described (短发、三无、魅惑、OL风) - not four different archetypes. He's saying \"全部来一张\" earlier was about the convo context showing my previous message where I said \"你要画哪个？OL、空姐、文学少女——还是全部来一张？😏\" - that was the conversation info showing my earlier question.\n\nSo he only wants ONE picture. The first one I spawned (OL goddess) is the right one. The other three (空姐, 文学少女, 旗袍) he didn't ask for - I misread the conversation context.\n\nI need to cancel the extra three Son tasks. But I can't cancel spawned subagents directly. Let me just let them finish and ignore the results, or I could try to cancel them. Actually, there's no tool to cancel a spawned subagent. I'll just tell 汀桑 that the extra three are already running and I can't stop them, but the OL one is the one he wanted.\n\nActually, the other three Son tasks (空姐, 文学少女, 旗袍) were spawned with mode=\"run\" which means they'll auto-announce their results to the user. That could be annoying - the user will get three extra images they didn't ask for.\n\nLet me check if there's a way to cancel these. I don't have a tool to kill subagent sessions. The extra three will just have to finish and I'll tell the user they were a mistake.\n\nHmm, let me just acknowledge the mistake and wait for the first (OL) one.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"啊……抱歉😓 我搞混了，以为你说「全部来一张」指的是四个格子都要画。\n\n就那张 OL 女神才是你要的。多余的让它们跑完吧，我拦不住了🙈"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":38064,"output":387,"cacheRead":11904,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":341,"totalTokens":50355,"cost":{"input":0.005328960000000001,"output":0.00010836000000000001,"cacheRead":0.000333312,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005770632}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780487520