{"type":"message","id":"af177a66","parentId":"0426e613","timestamp":"2026-06-03T11:58:26.087Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"So the DashScope configuration is in `openclaw.json` and it uses the environment variable `DASHSCOPE_API_KEY`. The key currently set is `sk-ff3…e82b` which returns 401 Unauthorized.\n\nThe user is asking \"我配的生成图像的模型现在配的是什么\" - what model is configured for image generation.\n\nLooking at the data:\n1. The DashScope provider is configured with `qwen3-vl-flash` as a model\n2. The DASHSCOPE_API_KEY env var is set to `sk-ff3…e82b`\n3. The API returns 401 - invalid API key\n\nSon's draw function was configured to use qwen3-vl-flash (which uses the DashScope API). The API key seems to be invalid or expired.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你配的图像模型是 **DashScope 通义千问 qwen3-vl-flash**，API Key 当前是 `sk-ff3e523...`。\n\n问题就是那个 Key 失效了，阿里那边返回 401。估计是你之前注册后过期了或者 Key 换过没更新。\n\n要换一下 Key 吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":623,"output":270,"cacheRead":62336,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":196,"totalTokens":63229,"cost":{"input":0.00008722000000000001,"output":0.00007560000000000001,"cacheRead":0.001745408,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0019082279999999999}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780487902614,"responseId":"fa4affa7-c75e-49da-9b1a-6d802ef5fbf4"}}
