{"type":"message","id":"b1dd1949","parentId":"aa315086","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:00:49.366Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Spirit's draw_function.md is very similar to Son's - it just says \"调用图像生成模型\" (call image generation model) but doesn't specify which one. The `model_used` field is a nullable text field.\n\nSo the draw function definition itself doesn't specify a specific model. It just says to call an image generation model. The model used seems to be determined by Son at runtime.\n\nLooking at the successful 空姐 task, it used `wanx2.1-t2i-turbo` (通义万相) which is Alibaba's actual image generation model. So Son was able to use wanx when the model override was not specified.\n\nThe problem is: when I specified `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash` as the model override, that forced Son to use qwen3-vl-flash (a VLM for understanding images) instead of wanx (the actual image generation model). And qwen3-vl-flash tried to use the DashScope API but failed with 401.\n\nBut wait - the successful 空姐 task was on deepseek model (not qwen3-vl), and deepseek Son figured out to use wanx2.1-t2i-turbo. The OL task was on qwen3-vl model and failed.\n\nSo the answer to the user's question is: The draw function definition in Spirit doesn't specify a specific model - it just says \"调用图像生成模型\". Son decides which model to use at runtime. The successful image generation used `wanx2.1-t2i-turbo` (通义万相), not `qwen3-vl-flash`.\n\nThe issue was that I overrode the model to `dashscope/qwen3-vl-flash` which is a VLM (vision-language model for understanding) not an image generation model, and that attempt failed.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Spirit 写的时候没指定具体模型，就说「调用图像生成模型」。Son 实际画成的那张（空姐）用的是 **wanx2.1-t2i-turbo**——通义万相，阿里正儿八经的画图模型。\n\n`qwen3-vl-flash` 是你看图用的，我之前强行指定那个去画图，当然挂了。\n\n所以你配的 Key  (`DASHSCOPE_API_KEY`) 是对的，只不过我指定错了模型。让 Son 自己选模型跑就行。"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":110,"output":507,"cacheRead":65024,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":391,"totalTokens":65641,"cost":{"input":0.0000154,"output":0.00014196,"cacheRead":0.001820672,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001978032}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780488044464,"responseId":"8c5fdf4c-495f-4bda-b8f3-f26b31f285cb"}}
