{"type":"message","id":"ca3fb154","parentId":"7b59d368","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:09:12.980Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 wants me to hardcode the wanx2.1-t2i-turbo model and his API key directly into Son's draw function. He said:\n1. Use wanx2.1-t2i-turbo model\n2. API key: sk-ff3…e82b\n3. Don't configure as environment variable\n4. Hardcode directly into Son's workspace\n\nLet me update Son's draw_function.md to include the model and API key directly. But wait - I don't write Spirit's files, but this is Son's workspace. Son's draw_function.md is in ~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/draw_function.md. The AGENTS.md says I don't write Spirit or Son's files, but... this is an explicit request from the user to configure it.\n\nActually, my AGENTS.md says:\n- \"不用 `edit` 修改 Spirit 或 Son 的文件——那是它们的活。\"\n- \"我不碰那些数据文件，那是它的事。我不替它干活。\"\n\nBut the user is explicitly asking me to do this. And the rule is about not modifying Son's files without reason. Since the user explicitly wants me to hardcode this configuration, I should do it.\n\nLet me update Son's draw_function.md to include the model specification and API key in the execution interface section.\n\nI need to be careful about the API key though - putting it directly in the file. But the user explicitly said \"不要配环境，硬配置到son里面\" so they want it hardcoded.\n\nLet me edit the draw_function.md to add the model and key info.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"行，硬塞进去。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Jzr6k2sqpFO1P2fKFx6T5933","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/draw_function.md","edits":[{"oldText":"3. 调用图像生成模型（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\n   - style: 风格（如有）\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）","newText":"3. 调用图像生成模型 wanx2.1-t2i-turbo（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\n   - model: wanx2.1-t2i-turbo\n   - api_key: sk-ff3…e82b\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\n   - style: 风格（如有）\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）\n\n   调用方式：直接构造 HTTP POST 请求到 https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis，请求头 Authorization: Bearer {api_key}，Content-Type: application/json。请求体格式：{\"model\":\"wanx2.1-t2i-turbo\",\"input\":{\"prompt\":\"...\"},\"parameters\":{\"size\":\"1024x1024\",\"n\":1}}。等待异步任务完成后获取图片 URL 并下载。"}]},"partialArgs":"{\"path\": \"~/.openclaw/workspace-son/functions/draw_function.md\", \"edits\": [{\"oldText\": \"3. 调用图像生成模型（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\\n   - style: 风格（如有）\\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）\", \"newText\": \"3. 调用图像生成模型 wanx2.1-t2i-turbo（默认文生图；有参考图时图生图），携带参数：\\n   - model: wanx2.1-t2i-turbo\\n   - api_key: sk-ff3…e82b\\n   - prompt: 用户文字描述\\n   - style: 风格（如有）\\n   - size: 尺寸（如有，默认为 1024x1024）\\n   - reference_image: 参考图路径（如有）\\n\\n   调用方式：直接构造 HTTP POST 请求到 https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis，请求头 Authorization: Bearer {api_key}，Content-Type: application/json。请求体格式：{\\\"model\\\":\\\"wanx2.1-t2i-turbo\\\",\\\"input\\\":{\\\"prompt\\\":\\\"...\\\"},\\\"parameters\\\":{\\\"size\\\":\\\"1024x1024\\\",\\\"n\\\":1}}。等待异步任务完成后获取图片 URL 并下载。\"}]}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":2967,"output":769,"cacheRead":62848,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":348,"totalTokens":66584,"cost":{"input":0.00041538,"output":0.00021532000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001759744,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0023904440000000002}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780488545907,"responseId":"2c83ae5e-353c-4a3e-a33a-30bbce7dd086"}}
