{"type":"message","id":"e78cc046","parentId":"2286cec4","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:10:27.788Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is pointing out that if the gateway restarts, the environment variable `DASHSCOPE_API_KEY` would be lost if it's only set in the shell environment. He's saying that hardcoding the key into Son's draw_function.md is fine because it's persistent in the file, but we just need to make sure the key is stored somewhere that survives restarts.\n\nWait, actually he said \"硬配置到son里面\" which is what I did - I put the key directly in the draw_function.md file. That IS persistent - it's in the file system. So even if the gateway restarts, the key is still in the file.\n\nBut he's asking \"那我网关重启不是key又拿不到了吗\" - \"if the gateway restarts, won't the key be lost?\" \n\nThat's only true if the key was stored as an environment variable. But I hardcoded it into Son's draw_function.md file, which is on disk. So it should survive restarts.\n\nBut wait - let me check what I actually did. I wrote:\n```\n- api_key: sk-ff3…e82b\n```\n\nThis is in the markdown file as documentation/instruction for Son. When Son reads this file, it needs to actually use this key to call the API. Son has to parse the markdown and extract the key, then use it in the curl call.\n\nThe instruction says:\n```\n调用方式：直接构造 HTTP POST 请求到 https://dashscope.aliyuncs.com/api/v1/services/aigc/text2image/image-synthesis，请求头 Authorization: Bearer {api_key}\n```\n\nSo Son would need to read this from the file. But the actual API key shown is `sk-ff3…e82b` - that's with an ellipsis because the env var output was truncated. Let me check what the actual full key is.\n\nActually, when I ran `env | grep DASHSCOPE_API_KEY`, the output was `DASHSCOPE_API_KEY=*** - the middle was truncated. So I don't have the full key.\n\nHmm, this is a problem. I wrote `sk-ff3…e82b` to the file, but that's the truncated version, not the full key.\n\nLet me get the full key.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"你说得对，但有个问题——我刚写进 Son 文件里的 `sk-ff3…e82b` 是截断的，不是完整 Key。让我先拿全的。"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_2S096D416IVL0O6noDiv3805","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"echo $DASHSCOPE_API_KEY"},"partialArgs":"{\"command\": \"echo $DASHSCOPE_API_KEY\"}"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3149,"output":580,"cacheRead":65536,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":489,"totalTokens":69265,"cost":{"input":0.00044086,"output":0.00016240000000000002,"cacheRead":0.001835008,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002438268}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1780488621967,"responseId":"9a9641ce-88cb-4770-8ce0-daf536d14604"}}
