{"type":"message","id":"6351ce3c","parentId":"12f1eaa0","timestamp":"2026-06-03T12:36:45.722Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"汀桑 is asking about the qwen-image-2.0 model - what level/quality it is. From the AliCloud docs I just fetched:\n\nqwen-image-2.0 is listed as:\n- 文生图: 支持\n- 编辑: 支持\n- 最大输出数: 6\n- 最大分辨率: 2048x2048\n\nIt's described as \"qwen-image-2.0-pro的快速版本\" (the fast version of qwen-image-2.0-pro).\n\nIt's part of the Qwen Image series, not the Wan series. So it's a different image generation model from Alibaba.\n\nLet me give him the comparison based on what I saw.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"`qwen-image-2.0` 是通义千问自家的图像模型，跟万相（Wan）两条线。\n\n看文档的数据：\n\n| 指标 | qwen-image-2.0 | wan2.7-image-pro | wanx2.1-t2i-turbo（你现在的） |\n|:--|:--:|:--:|:--:|\n| 文生图 | ✅ | ✅ | ✅（Legacy） |\n| 图片编辑 | ✅ | ✅ | ❌ |\n| 最大出图 | 6张 | 4张 | 4张 |\n| 最大分辨率 | 2048x2048 | 4096x4096 | 1440x1440 |\n| 负向提示词 | ❌（Pro版有） | ❌ | ❌ |\n\n`qwen-image-2.0` 定位是 **pro 的快速版**——比 pro 快很多，价格也低得多。但限制是不能用负向提示词。\n\n对比你现在的 wanx2.1-t2i-turbo：都是快速出图，但 qwen-image-2.0 支持编辑、分辨率更高、支持连续出 6 张。总体来说是升级。\n\n要改 def 用这个，还是上 wan2.7-image-pro？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":5697,"output":428,"cacheRead":73216,"cacheWrite":0,"reasoningTokens":149,"totalTokens":79341,"cost":{"input":0.0007975800000000001,"output":0.00011984,"cacheRead":0.002050048,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.002967468}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1780490201340,"responseId":"bcc8a48d-45c9-4d79-b28e-b4d87a1fac31"}}
